Kenny Everett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kenny_Everett 0 Maurice James Christopher Cole (25 December 1944 – 4 April 1995), known professionally as Kenny Everett, was a British comedian, radio DJ, and television entertainer. Everett is best known for his career as a radio DJ and for The Kenny Everett Video Show.
